<p>Welcome to CINEMA, your ultimate destination for the latest and greatest movies. Explore our collection, find your favorite films, and enjoy an unparalleled cinematic experience.</p>

<p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-area="" asp-controller="Movies" asp-action="Index">Browse Movies</a>
</p>

